{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a mobile-first educational statistics section for Ariya Supplements’ sleep product, Calm Nights.The design should feel premium, modern, and clean, similar to leading DTC wellness brands.Use Ariya’s purple branding, large bold statistics, plenty of white space, rounded corners, and a strong call-to-action button.Section Headline:Your Brain Wasn’t Designed For Modern Life.Supporting Text:Late-night scrolling. Constant notifications. Endless stimulation.Statistic #1:Visual Icon Instructions:
    Use a brain icon or brain silhouette in Ariya purple. 48%of U.S. adults report lying awake at night due to stress.Statistic #2:Visual Icon Instructions:
    Use three person silhouettes with one highlighted in Ariya purple to visually represent “1 in 3.” 1 in 3adults don’t get enough sleep on a regular basis.Statistic #3:Visual Icon Instructions:
    Use a moon icon in Ariya purple with subtle stars around it. 50–70 MillionAmericans struggle with ongoing sleep problems.Transition Text:Modern life makes it harder than ever to slow down and relax before bed.CTA Headline:That’s Why We Created Calm Nights.CTA Text:Melatonin-free sleep support designed to help quiet a racing mind, promote relaxation, and help you wake up refreshed.Button Text:Shop Calm NightsDesign Notes:Large statistic numbers should be the visual focus.Statistics should stack vertically on mobile.Do not use generic charts, graphs, arrows, pie charts, or abstract icons.Use only the specified icons for each statistic.Icons should feel premium, minimal, and luxury wellness oriented.Use Ariya purple accents throughout.Maintain a clean DTC wellness aesthetic.Keep the entire section easy to scan in under 5 seconds.Statistics should visually tell a story: Stress → Poor Sleep → Millions Struggling., Refine the Calm Nights statistics section to improve visual hierarchy, readability, and premium brand presentation.Overall GoalMake the section feel more like a premium wellness brand (Ritual, Eight Sleep, Momentous, AG1) and less like a template.The section should be extremely easy to scan in under 5 seconds on mobile.The statistics should be the main visual focus.Color ChangesReduce the amount of purple.Use the following hierarchy:HeadlineColor: BlackText:
    Your Brain Wasn’t Designed For Modern Life.Supporting TextColor: Dark GrayText:
    Late-night scrolling. Constant notifications. Endless stimulation.StatisticsKeep ONLY the large statistic numbers in Ariya purple.Examples:48%
    1 in 3
    50–70 MillionThese should remain the strongest visual elements in the section.Statistic DescriptionsUse dark gray or black.Example:48%of U.S. adults report lying awake at night due to stress.The description should not be purple.IconsUse a lighter purple or dark gray.Do NOT make icons the same bold purple as the statistics.Icons should support the information, not compete with it.CTA SectionKeep the button Ariya purple.Button should remain the strongest call-to-action on the page.Icon ChangesReplace the current icons.Do NOT use generic symbols, location pins, smiley faces, badges, or unrelated icons.Statistic 1Text:48%of U.S. adults report lying awake at night due to stress.Icon:Use ONE of these:Person lying awake in bedMoon above a bedBed with eyes openPurpose:Visually communicate difficulty sleeping due to stress.Statistic 2Text:1 in 3adults don’t get enough sleep on a regular basis.Icon:Use a group of 3 people with 1 highlighted.Purpose:The icon should visually communicate “1 in 3.”Do NOT use generic people icons.Statistic 3Text:50–70 MillionAmericans struggle with chronic sleep issues.Icon:Use a crowd of people icon.Examples:Multiple people grouped togetherCommunity iconCrowd silhouettePurpose:Visually communicate millions of people.Do NOT use:Location pinsMap markersBadgesAbstract symbolsCard StylingKeep cards clean and premium.White backgroundSubtle shadowRounded cornersPlenty of whitespaceStatistics should immediately stand out when scrolling.Mobile LayoutStack all three cards vertically.Each card should have:IconStatisticDescriptionWith generous spacing between each element.CTA SectionHeadline:That’s Why We Created Calm Nights.Body:Melatonin-free sleep support designed to help quiet a racing mind, promote relaxation, and help you wake up refreshed.Button:Shop Calm NightsKeep the button in Ariya purple.Button should be visually stronger than every other element except the statistics.Design Philosophy80% neutral colors.
    20% Ariya purple.Use purple only to draw attention to:StatisticsButtonSmall accent detailsEverything else should remain neutral so the important information stands out., Change only the icons for the 48% and 50–70 Million statistic cards. Do not redesign the section.
    
    For the 48% card, replace the current icon with a simple moon icon.
    
    For the 50–70 Million card, replace the current icon with a simple group of people icon.
    
    Keep the icons:
    
    minimal
    outline style
    dark gray or light Ariya purple
    centered above the statistic
    same size as the 1 in 3 icon
    Do not use:
    
    beds
    baskets
    circles
    abstract dot patterns
    location pins
    complex illustrations
    Use only:
    
    moon icon for 48%
    group of people icon for 50–70 Million
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-sleep-stats-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding_mobile }}px 20px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.background_color }};
  }

  .ai-sleep-stats-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: {{ block.settings.max_width }}px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .ai-sleep-stats-header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.header_spacing_mobile }}px;
  }

  .ai-sleep-stats-headline-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.headline_size_mobile }}px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: {{ block.settings.headline_color }};
    margin: 0 0 {{ block.settings.subtext_spacing }}px 0;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .ai-sleep-stats-subtext-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.subtext_size_mobile }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.subtext_color }};
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .ai-sleep-stats-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: {{ block.settings.stat_gap_mobile }}px;
    margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.transition_spacing_mobile }}px;
  }

  .ai-sleep-stat-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.card_background }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.card_border_radius }}px;
    padding: {{ block.settings.card_padding_mobile }}px;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: {{ block.settings.card_shadow }};
  }

  .ai-sleep-stat-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: {{ block.settings.icon_size_mobile }}px;
    height: {{ block.settings.icon_size_mobile }}px;
    margin: 0 auto {{ block.settings.icon_spacing }}px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .ai-sleep-stat-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    fill: {{ block.settings.icon_color }};
  }

  .ai-sleep-stat-number-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.stat_number_size_mobile }}px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: {{ block.settings.stat_number_color }};
    margin: 0 0 {{ block.settings.stat_description_spacing }}px 0;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .ai-sleep-stat-description-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.stat_description_size_mobile }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.description_color }};
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .ai-sleep-stats-transition-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.transition_size_mobile }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.subtext_color }};
    margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.cta_spacing_mobile }}px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .ai-sleep-stats-cta-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.cta_background }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.cta_border_radius }}px;
    padding: {{ block.settings.cta_padding_mobile }}px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .ai-sleep-stats-cta-headline-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.cta_headline_size_mobile }}px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: {{ block.settings.headline_color }};
    margin: 0 0 {{ block.settings.cta_text_spacing }}px 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .ai-sleep-stats-cta-text-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.cta_text_size_mobile }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.description_color }};
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0 0 {{ block.settings.cta_button_spacing }}px 0;
  }

  .ai-sleep-stats-button-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: {{ block.settings.button_padding_vertical }}px {{ block.settings.button_padding_horizontal }}px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.button_background }};
    color: {{ block.settings.button_text_color }};
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.button_border_radius }}px;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.button_text_size }}px;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .ai-sleep-stats-button-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.button_hover_background }};
    color: {{ block.settings.button_hover_text_color }};
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 750px) {
    .ai-sleep-stats-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding_desktop }}px 40px;
    }

    .ai-sleep-stats-header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.header_spacing_desktop }}px;
    }

    .ai-sleep-stats-headline-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.headline_size_desktop }}px;
    }

    .ai-sleep-stats-subtext-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.subtext_size_desktop }}px;
    }

    .ai-sleep-stats-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      flex-direction: row;
      gap: {{ block.settings.stat_gap_desktop }}px;
      margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.transition_spacing_desktop }}px;
    }

    .ai-sleep-stat-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      flex: 1;
      padding: {{ block.settings.card_padding_desktop }}px;
    }

    .ai-sleep-stat-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      width: {{ block.settings.icon_size_desktop }}px;
      height: {{ block.settings.icon_size_desktop }}px;
    }

    .ai-sleep-stat-number-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.stat_number_size_desktop }}px;
    }

    .ai-sleep-stat-description-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.stat_description_size_desktop }}px;
    }

    .ai-sleep-stats-transition-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.transition_size_desktop }}px;
      margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.cta_spacing_desktop }}px;
    }

    .ai-sleep-stats-cta-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: {{ block.settings.cta_padding_desktop }}px;
    }

    .ai-sleep-stats-cta-headline-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.cta_headline_size_desktop }}px;
    }

    .ai-sleep-stats-cta-text-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.cta_text_size_desktop }}px;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<div class="ai-sleep-stats-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="ai-sleep-stats-container-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    <div class="ai-sleep-stats-header-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
